The Venue | M&G Foodstuff Catering and Events

M&G Foodstuff is not your regular catering company we are a young dynamic food company with a unique approach.

We create vibrant, seasonal and health centric food with ALWAYS a focus on quality!

We work with the top producers, photographers and fashion labels in NYC and we are looking to grow our team with other like-minded individuals.

The Role:

We are looking for a passionate strong full time Sous Chefs who has had exposure to fast-paced high volume kitchens. Catering experience is highly preferred. 

This is a kitchen manager position and there is a high level of administration expected. You will be overseeing the daily kitchen production, managing staff, running kitchen teams at events, ordering and liaise with clients.

As Sous Chef at M&G Foodstuff you;

Must be able to work well under pressure and can work autonomously;
Have a broad range of kitchen skills in all sections including basic baking and pastry;
Have a passion for food and the hospitality industry;
Are ALWAYS punctual with NO exceptions;
Can follow instruction and carry out your daily tasks efficiently and cleanly;
Can communicate professionally with people and have great relationship building skills and also problem solving skills;
Pride yourself on your clean and professional appearance with impeccable personal hygiene;
Maintain consistent quality of work;
Must have food handlers certificate;
Must have experience with DOH inspections;
Must understand the product and vision of the company while striving to become better;
On Offer

Great salary plus company benefits;
2 consecutive days off;
Great hours, No nights or weekends
Cross training through multiple areas;
Ongoing training and development;
What we expect from you:

• Be you, be UNIQUE
• Deliver EXCEPTIONAL food quality LIKE NO OTHER
• MAKE a DIFFERENCE
• RESPECT everyone
• Celebrate the WINS
• ENJOY every day

